title: Scott Rogers hestitant, pocket stick, Kubotan, Kubaton or Kobuta
description:
Surprise Self Defense DVD with Scott Rogers
The Secrets of the Hand Held Hestitant

Learn how a six inches legal key chain (aka. hestitant, Kubotan, or pocket stick) 
can give the average person the striking power 
of a 250 pound trained martial artist in less than an hour training time. 
Learn basic strikes and techniques of this one of a kind awesome self 
defense instrument. Learn to release holds, deal with punches and disable
an attacker with a minimum of effort and strength.
